<p>Brooke married her latest husband David, a French singer and Baywatch star in 2011, after they welcomed their two children.</p>

<p>She filed for divorce in April 2018 and last year explained their co-parenting equation to Us Weekly: 'We have a beautiful relationship right now, which is really valuable.'</p>

<p>Brooke also has two daughters by her first husband, Extreme Makeover plastic surgeon Garth Fisher - Neriah, 20, and Sierra, 18.</p>
